<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>결제 성공</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/user_contact.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        /* 텍스트를 중앙에 배치하는 스타일 */
        .centered-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 80vh; /* 화면의 80% 높이를 사용 */
            text-align: center;
        }
        .centered-content h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .centered-content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .centered-content a {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .centered-content a:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header id="header">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="branding">
                <h1><a href="/"><span class="highlight">고딘</span> Go-Dein</a></h1>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li class="current"><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="service">서비스</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="service">유지보수</a>
                            <a href="#">제작상황</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="portfolio">포트폴리오</a></li>
                    <li ><a href="contact">문의하기</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="contact">견적 문의</a>
                            <a href="support">고객지원</a>
                        </div></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <div class="user-menu">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <a href="#" id="user-name"><%= user.name %>님</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="/myinfo">내 정보</a>
                            <a href="/contracts">계약내용</a>
                            <a href="#" id="logout">로그아웃</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="login-button-container">
                        <a href="/login" class="login-btn">로그인</a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="centered-content">
    <h1>결제가 성공적으로 완료되었습니다!</h1>
    <p>주문 번호: <%= orderId %></p>
    <p>감사합니다. 결제가 정상적으로 처리되었습니다.</p>
    <a href="/">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
